#

Pan-Seared Duck Breast with Cherry Reduction and Creamy Polenta

$35.5
750 kcal
Difficulty: 75%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-free

Tags:

gourmetspecial occasionfrench cuisine

Description

Juicy duck breast paired with a sweet cherry reduction and creamy polenta for a rich and satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • Duck Breasts: 2 pieces
  • Cherries (pitted): 1 cup
  • Red Wine: 1/2 cup
  • Chicken Stock: 1 cup
  • Butter: 4 tablespoons
  • Cream: 1/2 cup
  • Polenta: 1 cup
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Shallots: 2, finely chopped
